{"tid":466800,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"自動上鍊錶盒討論區","createTime":"2017-11-13T02:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T02:09:37.000Z","uid":155254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a61fbd5ca59f34e7df1fca2ea312a140e994c221","tid":466800,"uid":155254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"好似唔多人討論過自動上鍊錶盒. 咁我就拋磚引玉啦.<br />\n<br />\n如果你喺帶開同或者有幾隻自動或手動錶既, 成日要較錶都幾麻煩. 而且聽講如果手錶長時間唔喐動會加快機油和潤滑劑的老化速度. 所以自動上鍊錶盒就應運而生. <br />\n<br />\n其實買自動上鍊錶盒要小心選擇. 唔同機芯有唔同上鍊要求. 甚麼雙向, 順時針,逆時針同每天幾多轉 (TPD - Turns Per Day) 都要考慮到. 自動上唔到鍊事小. 如果上壞隻錶就事大.有興趣可以到這個網站睇睇 (<a href=\"http://orbita.com/2010_web/NEW/Database-R.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forbita.com%2F2010_web%2FNEW%2FDatabase-R.htm&d=Xs2FPd0dkpmkrhVj0JzCg0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ff88fead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orbita.com/2010_web/NEW/Database-R.htm</a>).<br />\n<br />\n自動上鍊錶盒好似有好多選擇. 淘寶兩舊水又有. 或者可能個盒仲貴過隻錶既又有.<br />\n<br />\n我自己用開下面呢個. 有三個獨立調教.  用咗幾年覺得唔錯. 好靜. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/073344_140ceed09dd6493e1a479cca0656a18f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F073344_140ceed09dd6493e1a479cca0656a18f.jpg&h=53abe7ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712a7e5c130ca27b3a3722d1a05399ed5129891e","tid":466800,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"平平哋有乜揀？<br />\n想送畀人<br />\n之前送過隻畀人<br />\n佢唔係日日戴時間成日唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5ec5920faa3d3519d127f3f23f604e660ee9ea","tid":466800,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:14:40.000Z","msg":"原本想買一個個獨立用，但係又要好多個電位，但係一買三四個位嘅，又唔知自己會唔會再買錶&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de001919e095b90035e79024d23362f333e5da4f","tid":466800,"uid":155254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原本想買一個個獨立用，但係又要好多個電位，但係一買三四個位嘅，又唔知自己會唔會再買錶&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家好多 Modular Winder 可以一個個獨立買只要一個電源. 一個個買喺貴啲但有彈性.  好似下面呢個:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wolf1834.com/category/modular-winders/watch-winders/filter:watch_cnt(1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolf1834.com%2Fcategory%2Fmodular-winders%2Fwatch-winders%2Ffilter%3Awatch_cnt%281&d=Xs2FPd0dkpmkrhVj0JzCg0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ae4e5720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wolf1834.com/category/modular-winders/watch-winders/filter:watch_cnt(1</a>)/"},{"pid":"68e4e11d4a6a00837c21165fd745df253e702c9f","tid":466800,"uid":155254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"Wolf Modular 4.1. 好靚同好靜. 最多可以加到八個用同一電源. 因為個 cover 係銀色, 比我個 Viceroy 醒目好多. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/025820_1d583e868241cdeb66708cb38ad5c25e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F025820_1d583e868241cdeb66708cb38ad5c25e.jpg&h=c3827a35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de0ad183adf39371a8fb08b23ad13f135e309883","tid":466800,"uid":121924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"依排上網到個荷蘭牌子叫Bensen 唔知佢好定Wolf好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cae84bf10a88b69cd54055559580b78c795ec18","tid":466800,"uid":159476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ba6252d2e9070388fa5e9b74c29d3f019bf7900","tid":466800,"uid":155254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個網站好多錶都無/.\\<br />\n<br />\n例如VC 隻4500V</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVC 4